{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/04/02/docker化的mongodb使用方案.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8d79d847-3fe4-5cef-9e25-2ebabc15cdc0","excerpt":"docker 化的 mongodb 使用方案 之前提到过使用 watchtower 更新本地的 image 的方案，本来我的系统一直使用 sqlite 来做数据库，现在想改成 mongodb。 涉及到 mongodb 就不得不需要考虑怎么本地化，并且如何做备份。数据本地化很好做，只需要 docker 的 volume…","html":"<h1>docker 化的 mongodb 使用方案</h1>\n<p>之前提到过<a href=\"/tech/2020/03/15/Coding.net%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Jenkins%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2CI&#x26;CD\">使用 watchtower 更新本地的 image 的方案</a>，本来我的系统一直使用 sqlite 来做数据库，现在想改成 mongodb。</p>\n<p>涉及到 mongodb 就不得不需要考虑怎么本地化，并且如何做备份。数据本地化很好做，只需要 docker 的 volume 即可，编写<code class=\"language-text\">docker-compose.yml</code>，使用<code class=\"language-text\">docker-compose up -d</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-ini line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-ini\">version: '3.7'\n\nvolumes:\n  mongo:\n  strapi:\n\nservices:\n  mongo:\n    image: mongo\n    restart: always\n    volumes:\n      - mongo:/data/db\n    ports:\n      - 27017:27017\n  adminmongo:\n    image: mrvautin/adminmongo\n    ports:\n      - 1234:1234\n    environment:\n      - HOST<span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>0.0.0.0</span>\n      - CONN_NAME<span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>mongo</span>\n      - DB_HOST<span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>mongo</span>\n      - DB_PORT<span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>27017</span>\n      - PASSWORD<span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>$ADMIN_MONGO_PASSWORD</span>\n    links:\n      - mongo:mongo\n  strapi:\n      image: &lt;strapi registry>\n      environment:\n        DATABASE_CLIENT: mongo\n        DATABASE_NAME: strapi\n        DATABASE_HOST: mongo\n        DATABASE_PORT: 27017\n      links:\n        - mongo:mongo\n      volumes:\n        - ./app:/srv/app\n      ports:\n        - '1337:1337'</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>备份</h2>\n<p>使用如下命令备份</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker-compose <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> -T mongo mongodump --archive --gzip --db <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>database<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> dump.gz</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>还原</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker-compose <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> -T mongo mongorestore --archive --gzip <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> dump.gz</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>可视化管理 docker</h2>\n<p>使用 <a href=\"https://www.portainer.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">portainer</a> 能够可视化管理现在运行的 docker。执行如下命令，再访问 localhost:9000，嗒嗒！以后再也不需要执行<code class=\"language-text\">docker ps</code>了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker run -d -p <span class=\"token number\">8000</span>:8000 -p <span class=\"token number\">9000</span>:9000 --name<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>portainer --restart<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>always -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v portainer_data:/data portainer/portainer</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>可视化管理 mongodb</h2>\n<p>可以使用<a href=\"https://github.com/mrvautin/adminMongo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">adminmongo</a>提供一套简单可用的 WebUI，我已经写到了 docker compose 里面了。</p>\n<p>另外<code class=\"language-text\">environment</code>里面的<code class=\"language-text\">PASSWORD</code>并不好使，已经有<a href=\"https://github.com/mrvautin/adminMongo/issues/166\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">issue</a>，不过已经是 2017 年的了，最快的解决方式就是删除<code class=\"language-text\">config/app.json</code>，只需要在 portainer 里面选择<code class=\"language-text\">Containers &gt; mongodb_adminmongo_1</code> 点击 <code class=\"language-text\">Edit</code>，修改 <code class=\"language-text\">Command</code> 并重新部署。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/be8ee/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.48648648648649%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/cbe2e/2020-04-02-portainer-config.webp 148w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/3084c/2020-04-02-portainer-config.webp 295w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/5ca24/2020-04-02-portainer-config.webp 590w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/dad35/2020-04-02-portainer-config.webp 885w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/2baf0/2020-04-02-portainer-config.webp 1180w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/712a0/2020-04-02-portainer-config.webp 1552w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/a80bd/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg 148w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/1c91a/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg 295w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/1c72d/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg 590w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/a8a14/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg 885w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/fbd2c/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg 1180w,\n/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/be8ee/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg 1552w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/f081c6cc2378ea441c3dadd8474c78a2/1c72d/2020-04-02-portainer-config.jpg\"\n          alt=\"portainer的设置\"\n          title=\"portainer的设置\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">portainer的设置</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/04/02/docker化的mongodb使用方案.html","date":"April 02, 2020","title":"docker化的mongodb使用方案"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/04/02/docker化的mongodb使用方案.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2020/03/31/2020年Q1总结.html","title":"2020年Q1总结"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}},"next":null}}}